ers like cystic fibrosis, muscle dystrophy, hemophilia, and a number of oth=
er common and rate genetic disorders. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64=
); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Fun little asid=
e here: when I was 2 years old, CHOP doctors saved my life. I had an atrial=
 septal defect &#8212; a hole in my heart &#8212; that required pretty inva=
